# EXISTING STRUCTURES

# ERROR TIPS

### Inventory full when harvesting
- Ensure that the agent has enough space in its inventory before attempting to harvest items.

### Could not extract due to missing entity
- The agent attempted to extract `iron-plate` from position (0.0, 0.0), but there was no valid entity containing `iron-plate` at that location. Ensure that the target entity exists and contains the specified item before attempting to extract.
